flowchart TD
  subgraph DataSources
    S5[TROPOMI]
    INS[INSAT-3D]
    ERA[ERA5]
    FIR[FIRMS]
    CPC[CPCB]
  end

  S5 --> DL[Downloaders & Collectors: src/data/*_download*.py]
  INS --> DL
  ERA --> DL
  FIR --> DL
  CPC --> DL

  DL --> FE[Feature Engineering: build_dataset_aqi.py / build_dataset_hcho.py]
  FE --> STORE[data/processed/*.csv / netCDF]
  STORE --> SEQ[Sequence generation: sliding-window, context features]
  SEQ --> TRAIN[Train Pipeline: src/models/train_aqi.py]
  TRAIN --> CKPT[Saved checkpoint — .pt]
  TRAIN --> EVAL[Evaluation & metrics]
  EVAL --> EXPORT[Export predictions, GeoJSON, netCDF]
  EXPORT --> DASH[Dashboard & Visualization: src/webapp/app.py]
  STORE --> DASH

  subgraph Automation
    PIPE[Orchestrator: scripts/run_pipeline.py]
  end

  PIPE --> DL
  PIPE --> FE
  PIPE --> TRAIN
